        "content": "<p> The reference to the single cry is understood by some commentators to mean that the Gathering will occur almost instantly. This is buttressed by other verses that affirm the immediacy of God’s command taking effect: “Our command is nothing but a single [word], like the blinking of an eye” (The Moon, 54:50) and: “The matter of the Hour’s [coming] is like the blink of an eye or nearer still” (The Bee, 16:77).  </p>",
